The People vs. Larry Flynt;;80;;88;;R;;Pursued by opponents who say his "Hustler" magazine breaks decency laws, pornographer Larry Flynt (Woody Harrelson) hires lawyer Alan Isaacman (Edward Norton) to help fight his legal battles. A zealot shoots the men near a Georgia courthouse, and though Flynt discovers he'll never walk again, his fighting spirit -- like his love for stripper Althea Leasure (Courtney Love) -- stays strong. Ultimately, the unlikely free speech warrior takes his biggest case to a showdown at the Supreme Court.;;Drama;;Milos Forman;;1996;;Woody Harrelson,Courtney Love,Ed Norton,James Cromwell,Crispin Glover,James Carville,Brett Harrelson,Donna Hanover,Norm Macdonald,Vincent Schiavelli,Miles Chapin,Richard Paul,D'Army Bailey,Burt Neuborne,Jan Tr√≠ska,Cody Block,Ryan Post,Robert Davis,Kacky Walton,John Saint Ryan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/people_vs_larry_flynt